  * debian/control:
    + update debhelper dependency to >= 7.
    + set myself as maintainer and Ole as uploader.
  * debian/rules:
    + use dh(7) style file with autoreconf add-on.
  * debian/doc-base:
    + properly register the documentation with doc-base.

